reviewText: This is an excellent DVD. A friend and I use to see him in concert in the 70s. I enjoyed the interview at the end. After I watched it I texted a friend about it.

This is awesome. I went to a couple of concerts of his and my enjoyment factor was sky-high. This is my first upgrade from vinyl records that disappeared somewhere along the way.. Listening and watching is taking a step back in time. If you enjoy quality rocking blues then this dvd is the answer.
Awesome show, better picture than I thought!
Any Edgar Winter fan would find this dvd great. it was extra special with his wife Monique with him on the extras. Very enjoyable.
